This is beta2 of the aim_ak-colt2 that i previously added to CSB several months ago. Nothing has really changed except the lighting and shadows. I did add 1 scout per side on top, and smoke grenades in the other building.

This map is bot ready.

**DO NOT EDIT OR CHANGE ANY PARTS OF THIS MAP WITHOUT MY PERMISSION
